&nbsp;
&nbsp;
<div </div
&nbsp;
&nbsp; In New York, with the Vice-President of the Chamber, there are several representatives of Italian Regions and Cities who were on their way overseas: in addition to the President of the Tuscany Region Eugenio Giani, will attend the commemorative events, today and tomorrow, the governor of Friuli Venezia Giulia (region guest of honor of the Gala 2024 of the Niaf) Massimiliano Fedriga and the Mayor of Palermo, Roberto Lagalla, in New York to promote the new air connection directed with the island but especially the 400 years of the Patroness of Palermo, Santa Rosalia, equally venerated in the Big Apple. (AGI)
